{
  "stem": "24195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I stayed there, until-- and then on-- How did you survive in the few month-- how long did you stay there?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the people in the house helped me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- I-- I-- I got them to believe me that I was discharged and that I was-- because of sickness, for medical reasons.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had-- were sympathetic to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They shared with me whatever-- when I needed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I stayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah, oh yeah, they were OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- yeah, they didn't know about us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't know that I was a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never told them about it, even when we first moved in there, before I was-- you know, called into the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then on April 16th-- I remember that distinctly-- 1945, the Russians had gathered all their forces, about 2 million men, for the final assault on Berlin.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the price-- the price-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The final price, the most coveted target, you know, the-- and they were the one-- you know, that was the-- the capital of Nazi Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's going to be a capital again of the new Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was-- and by-- by bad planning, the Allied-- Americans, British, French-- left the capture of Berlin to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they had the-- that was their-- that was their-- their move.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So April 16th, they started to come across the river, 2-million-men-strong army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was no way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's-- they went around and circled all Berlin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A few of the Nazi people got away the last day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember lookin' for food and going out and really taking a chance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Only we-- when you're 18 years old, you don't realize when there's real danger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had a bicycle down in the-- in the basement of that house.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
